    </p>

    <h3>Nov 13, 2023 — OSU President Jayathi Y. Murthy withdrawal letter</h3>
    <p>
      OSU President Jayathi Y. Murthy's letter formally withdrawing Oregon State
      University from its proposed role overseeing the Elliott State Research
      Forest — a turning point in the ESRF record.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-YBi1ICLiFxTKneEB6tud26B-_m3suKe/view?usp=drive_link" rel="noopener" target="_blank">PDF →</a> ·
